menu "breadboard: bb_dispatch_cmd"

config BB_DISPATCH_CMD_CAP
    int "Command dispatch table capacity"
    default 32
    help
        Maximum number of registered actions in the static dispatch table.
        Each entry costs sizeof(bb_dispatch_cmd_entry_t) (a function pointer
        + context pointer + action string pointer). Registering more actions
        than this returns BB_ERR_NO_SPACE (logged, non-fatal).

endmenu
